23:["$","section",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold mb-6","children":"The Problem: Why Missed Calls Cost UK Trades Thousands"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":["Before diving into the solutions, let us understand the scale of the problem. A typical UK ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/ai-call-answering-plumbers","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"plumber"}],"receives 8–12 calls per day, of which 5–7 go unanswered while they are under a sink, on a roof, or driving between jobs. At an average job value of £180–£400, each missed call represents a potential £90–£200 in lost revenue (accounting for the 50% of enquiries that convert to booked jobs)."]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":"Multiply that by 5 working days, and you are looking at £450–£1,000 per week in lost revenue. Over a year, that is £23,400–£52,000 for a single plumber. For a multi-van operation, the numbers scale linearly. The ONS data confirms this: 62% of calls to small UK businesses go unanswered, and the Federation of Small Businesses (FSB) estimates that missed calls cost UK small businesses £1,200 per year on average — but for trades with higher job values, the figure is significantly higher."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":"The traditional solutions have clear limitations. Voicemail is essentially a graveyard for enquiries — 78% of callers who reach voicemail do not leave a message. Call forwarding to a family member is unreliable and unprofessional. Hiring a human receptionist costs £20,000–£25,000 per year plus National Insurance, pension contributions, and holiday cover. For a sole trader or small team, these options are either ineffective or economically impossible."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"AI call answering services emerged as the practical solution. They answer every call, 24/7, without sick days, holidays, or wage demands. They qualify leads, capture contact details, and deliver enquiries instantly. The question is not whether you need one — it is which one is right for your specific trade business."}]]}]
