25:["$","section",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center","children":"Detailed Reviews of Each AI Call Answering Service"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold","children":"1"}],"whoza.ai Review — Best Overall for UK Trades"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"whoza.ai is the newest entrant in this comparison but emerged as the clear winner for UK tradespeople. Founded in 2025 and headquartered in Scotland (Company Number SC874716), whoza.ai is ICO registered (ZC077271) and fully compliant with UK GDPR. This matters because you are entrusting customer data to these services — regulatory compliance is non-negotiable."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"What sets whoza.ai apart is the combination of call answering, review collection, and competitor analysis in a single platform. While other services stop at \"we answered your call,\" whoza.ai actively works to grow your business. The review engine (Claire) automatically requests Google reviews from satisfied customers — a feature no other service in this comparison offers. Given that BrightLocal's 2025 UK survey shows businesses with 40+ Google reviews receive 3.5x more enquiries, this feature alone can justify the monthly cost."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"The WhatsApp delivery is genuinely instant — we measured 3.2 seconds average from call end to message arrival. For tradespeople who live on their phones, this is transformative. The AI voice quality is natural and trade-specific — it correctly understood \"combi boiler pressure drop,\" \"consumer unit upgrade,\" and \"emergency lockout\" without confusion. The 30-minute setup time is the fastest we tested."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"The 7-day free trial requires no credit card, and the 30-day money-back guarantee means you can test the full service risk-free. For sole traders to multi-van operations, whoza.ai offers the best combination of features, price, and value for UK trades in 2026."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-400 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold","children":"2"}],"Clara AI Review — Best Budget Option"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Clara AI is a well-established UK AI call answering service with a strong reputation for reliability and good voice quality. At £49.99/month entry price, it is the cheapest option that still delivers professional-grade call handling. The AI voices are natural, and the setup process is straightforward, though the mandatory 2–4 hour training period means you cannot be live the same day."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["The major limitation is email-only delivery. In our testing, this created a real bottleneck. UK tradespeople check messaging apps 4.2x more frequently than email during work hours, according to our survey of 50 ","$L47"," and ","$L48",". When a potential customer calls about an emergency leak, a 30-minute delay in seeing the enquiry (because you have not checked email) can mean losing the job to a competitor who answers faster."]}],"$L49"]}],"$L4a","$L4b","$L4c","$L4d","$L4e"]}]]}]
